page.title: 17A DAY IN MY LIFE 2
page.content: ON SATURDAY I GOT UP AT 8.00 AND HAD BREAKFAST GOT WASHED, CLEANED MY TEETH AND COMBED MY HAIR. AT 9.00 I WATCHED T.V. THEN WE WENT TO AN INTERVILLAGE TOURNAMENT. I PLAYED FOOTBALL FOR GREAT ELLINGHAM F.C.ARE FIRST GAME WE LOST 1.0 . ARE SECOND GAME WE LOST 1.0.I DID NOT PLAY IN THE FIRST TWO GAMES. THE LAST GAME I PLAYED WE LOST AGAIN 3.2. AT 12.00 WE HAD DINNER UNTIL 2.00PM THEN THE TOURNAMENT STARTED AGAIN. AFTER OUR LAST GAME WE WENT SWIMMING. WE WENT HOME AT ABOUT 5.00. FOR TEA WE HAD A BARBECUE .I HAD 2 BEEF BURGERS. AT 6.00 I PLAYED WITH MY FRIEND IAN UNTIL 7.30 THEN I WENT HOME. AT HOME I WATCHED TELEVISION UNTIL 9.00 THEN I WENT TO BED.I READ A BOOK FOR A BIT THEN I WENT TO SLEEP.
